POD2::IT version 0.07
=====================

POD2::IT - Italian translation of Perl core documentation.

See 'perldoc POD2::IT' for more info.

See pod2it.sf.net for more details about the project.

CHANGES FROM PREVIOUS VERSION

	! Updated perlboot.pod to 5.8.7 [osfameron]
	! Updated perlfunc.pod to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlfaq[1..9] to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlrequick to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Added all nicknames contributors to Changes/README and so on [bepi]

See 'Changes' file for complete history revisions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module doesn't require other modules and libraries.

